summary: This document appears to be an FBI evidence inventory record listing a seized hard drive containing multiple images, likely from the Epstein investigation. It references specific FBI evidence numbers and a hard drive serial number.
keyFacts: FBI seized a Western Digital hard drive (serial number WDC3003FZEX-0024SA0) on August 21, 2019.
The hard drive contained multiple images referenced by specific evidence numbers (NYCO23578 through NYCO23592).
The document is an official FBI evidence inventory record, indicating preservation of digital evidence in the Epstein case.
